untry deaths. The insights yielded by\nthis framework can be used to guide equitable vaccine distribution in future\npandemics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2023 22:08:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-13"}
